Electronic Products

At UBA, we understand your need to have your money on the go. That is why we designed a suite of convenient and secure virtual and mobile banking products just for you. These include:

  • U-Direct (Internet Banking)

  • U-Mobile (Mobile Banking)

  • E-Statements

  • Wise Alert

  • Integrity Statement

  • Telephone Banking

  • U-Card
